    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >We need you, Pilot!</h2><br>Do you love <strong>Exoblast</strong>?<br>Here's one way to support the game: grab the &quot;<strong>Vampire Skins</strong>&quot; pack and allow the development team to continue developing the game!<br>Every support pack comes with exclusive skins and announcer!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exoblast is 100% free!</h2><br>We wanted to make a fun and eye-catching first game.<br>But above all, we wanted to bring together a large community of passionate players.<br>Exoblast needs players and for that what better than a <strong>free </strong>game?<br><br>You like the game and want to thank the development team, help us, keep Exoblast servers online?<br>Whatever your reason, you are there to <strong>support us</strong> and we thank you very much!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811100/extras/4eba737d9654df974cedbac35084919e.poster.avif?t=1643707446\" width=512 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811100/extras/4eba737d9654df974cedbac35084919e.webm?t=1643707446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811100/extras/4eba737d9654df974cedbac35084919e.mp4?t=1643707446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This pack will give you <strong>vampire skins</strong>, so you can drink the blood of your enemies.<br>Enjoy the demonic announcer and scare the hell out of your opponent!<br><br>We are counting on you, <strong>Pilot</strong>!",
